data.post:
Initiative Q is an attempt by ex-PayPal guys to create a new payment system instead of credit cards that were designed in the 1950s. The system uses its own currency, the Q, and to get people to start using the system once it's ready they are allocating Qs for free to people that sign up now (the amount drops as more people join - so better to join early). Signing up is free and they only ask for your name and an email address. There's nothing to lose but if this payment system becomes a world leading payment method your Qs can be worth a lot. If you missed getting bitcoin seven years ago, you wouldn't want to miss this.

Here is my invite link: https://initiativeq.com/invite/Hl1QJxA2m

 This link will stop working once Iâm out of invites. Let me know after you registered, because I need to verify you on my end.

Hey lads,

A few reminders before the poker night kicks off.

We will start playing at 8 pm but everyone needs to register before we start playing. To get everyone registered on time it is important to arrive 30 minutes early. 

Dress code smart casual (Blazers, Shirts).

There are 4 tables, 2 in the VIP and 2 upstairs. Drinking will only be permitted in the VIP room. I was told no hard liquors so It is not recommended. 

The seating allocation will go in order of people who have first confirmed their spaces. The game will be played as a tournament format so as people are knocked out  they will be filling in the spaces in the VIP room. If you are knocked out within the first hour you are welcome to buy back in for 5 quid.

We will all get a â¬10 free bet when we sight up. half the earning from these bets will go toward the pot and half towards SVDP charity

Looking forward to seeing most of you there.

Hello gentlemen, this group has been set up for those who have been selected to take part in the rush process for the Theta Omicron chapter of the Zeta Psi fraternity.

As rush chair I will be using this page to inform you of the rush procedure and event plans. You should also feel free to use this page to ask me any questions you may have about the fraternity or the rush procedure or dm me.

To start off I would like to tell you about our plan for the coming week

This Wednesday the 3rd we will having a night in Hideout pool on South William Street. It's 10 euro for 2.5 hours from 8:30-11pm and it's BYOB so bring cans, nags, your a-game etc.w

When making the decision on whether you will be a member, you're attendance will be considered. However if you have a legitimate excuse for missing an event do let me know.

Enjoy it lads! 
All the best

Mathieux
